[Course_Description]
When you're working in a team, you need to think of productivity as a team effort. In his 2018 book Smart Teams, Dermot Crowley provides tools and strategies designed to help leaders create a more productive work culture. This audiobook summary distills those lessons into bite-sized tips for working smarter as a team. Learn how to clearly communicate your message, collaborate more effectively, and build a more harmonious team environment. Note: This audiobook summary was produced by Blinkist. We are pleased to host this content in our library.